{"tid":2216822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭稱GNMIS是客觀平台界定傳媒 毛孟靜斥擘大眼講大話","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T07:03:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8ef5d732478091deebf0faaecd2e811b64a3e6","tid":2216822,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077667&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=8a01e15c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077667&h=ef7a39ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077667</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）警方修改《警隊通例》中「傳媒代表」的定義，只承認已登記政府新聞處新聞發布系統（GNMIS）的媒體。林鄭月娥於昨發文力撐，支持警方採用GNMIS「這個客觀、開放、一視同仁的服務平台來界定誰是傳媒代表。」立法會議員毛孟靜斥林鄭再一次「擘大眼講大話」，民主黨許智峯則斥GNMIS是一套不公平、有門檻的系統。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥昨晚於 Facebook 帖文回應警方修改「傳媒代表」定義，表示要「不吐不快」。她稱GNMIS是「客觀、開放、一視同仁的服務平台」，支持警方以此界定誰是「傳媒代表」。林鄭月娥又表示，她上任後容許「純網上媒體」登記使用系統，至今有30個網媒成為用戶。"},{"pid":"5628254479be938fd3eb52b5a026bb0eb583e1a6","tid":2216822,"uid":305767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呀？咁點解外國已登記媒體又都畀狗列為非登記媒體呀？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你諗住搞個除名機制出黎畀狗用，你又覺得我地唔知？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />7婆，你條粉皮！出D新D既橋得唔得？鬼唔知你最尾咩都畀狗管！"},{"pid":"6a91a2d1a111878ea636658c363c1efb8082ad90","tid":2216822,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54b91566fa86274450a410a13a445fbcca8a06c","tid":2216822,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a91a2d1a111878ea636658c363c1efb8082ad90","tid":2216822,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"將來光復一定要肅清呢類畜牲"}]}